content:
The #BuildBackBetter Act would close the Medicaid coverage gap for 3 years, providing subsidized #ACA marketplace coverage to 2.2M uninsured people in 12 states. 

But providing a permanent pathway to coverage may fall back to states in the long-term. https://t.co/ITOR8A6DhC
